Titolo: Heron: Steam Machine

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Heron: Steam Machine is a puzzle video game by Triangle Studios, released for WiiWare and iOS. It is a new take on the Pipe Mania concept, adding arcade elements such as multiplayer gameplay and changing the format to a filled board with rotatable blocks rather than being able to place new blocks on the board.



Genere: Puzzle 

Valutazione: 70
